Package jester

Class JesterKeys

java.lang.Object
jester.JesterKeys
public class JesterKeys extends Object
JesterKeys is a static helper class that defines readable constants for keyboard keys using java.awt.event.KeyEvent values. This allows developers to use key names like JesterKeys.SPACE instead of KeyEvent.VK_SPACE in their code, improving readability.
